{"tid":1775472,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"世正被偶像IU翻牌！ 演唱獲讚「像畫一樣」…","createTime":"2019-12-09T01:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T20:14:50.000Z","uid":74065,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5926690ad1c02b2d24be74dfbd92b20238ad3e3","tid":1775472,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T01:21:37.000Z","msg":"南韓歌手金世正長相甜美、歌唱實力堅強，她從《PRODUCE 101》脫穎而出，先後成為女團I.O.I、gu9udan成員，2016年推出SOLO曲《花路》摘下了音源榜冠軍，日前睽違3年再度推出新歌《隧道》也獲得好評。她日前上了南韓音樂訪談節目《柳熙烈的寫生簿》翻唱了IU的《above the time》，竟獲得原唱的青睞，轉發在IU本人的IG上，讓她開心不已。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4563/d4563564.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4563%2Fd4563564.jpg&h=16e4482b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金世正翻唱IU歌曲。（圖／翻攝IU、金世正 IG）<br />\n<br />\nIU日前在IG限時動態分享了金世正於節目上的演唱片段，寫下「好像一幅畫」，作為原唱，不吝地給予了後輩稱讚與鼓勵。而金世正在不久後也將她的限時動態截圖，為此發了一篇貼文，寫道：「我上輩子做了什麼嗎？救了國家？統一了三國？發明了隱形眼鏡跟炸雞？」成為了「追星成功」的又一典範。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4563/d4563565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4563%2Fd4563565.jpg&h=da4e48b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU限時動態分享金世正的演唱影片。（圖／翻攝IU IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4563/d4563566.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4563%2Fd4563566.jpg&h=54c14f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金世正截圖IU限時動態發文。（圖／翻攝金世正 IG）<br />\n<br />\n網友在看完兩人暖暖的互動後，也紛紛回應「偶像的偶像IU」、「兩個人的版本都超好聽」、「世正好可愛啊」、「恭喜世正追星成功！」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6aB1LG3Q6z0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6aB1LG3Q6z0&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=a6c8ca98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6aB1LG3Q6z0</a><br />\n▲金世正翻唱IU歌曲《above the time》。（影片取自YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒。）"},{"pid":"8ab3d695ee48ec5250f7d5c4cdba7e826b9c286d","tid":1775472,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,